{"tid":1986062,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SJ利特發文警告駭客：「每天每天 好像都被盜帳號 請停止吧」","createTime":"2020-04-23T14:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T18:27:23.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c5115db69f1de6894196048a3d2a067cb3f95d","tid":1986062,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"Super Junior隊長利特今日（23日）在IG上傳了一張照片。<br />\n<br />\n並寫下：「每天每天 #好像都被盜帳號 #請停止吧 #真的收到非常多簡訊 #請停止吧。」照片是instagram方面傳送的提示更換密碼的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_00571d13a953e9cea78b496d1a9360c6/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-23/126170-834319.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_00571d13a953e9cea78b496d1a9360c6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-23%2F126170-834319.png&h=9ea4ad33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少粉絲看到也表示：「不要再盜帳號了」、「到底為什麼要盜別人的帳號」、「不要再打擾他了」、「太煩了...有完沒完啊」、「他平常以經很心苦了，不要再做這種事了」、「希望大家可以善良一點」等等。<br />\n<br />\n利特在2月直播時，透露電話號碼被洩露的事情，一直深受攻擊的困擾。之前也曾說過：「現在已經不驚訝了，反正又很快會被洩露出去的，這是經常會發生的事情，換電話號碼的話馬上又會打電話過來的時代。」"},{"pid":"7641c8735b180b9e0e82ef25aa0071056de52fb5","tid":1986062,"uid":202591,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"妍雨啊..."},{"pid":"6a29c2929b4bb9785a1653455832ee8f2bf28fff","tid":1986062,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"妍雨阿..."},{"pid":"9b014af880b89d5f1ed13c62fb5748de6b310e64","tid":1986062,"uid":22591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7641c8735b180b9e0e82ef25aa0071056de52fb5","tid":1986062,"uid":202591,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"妍雨啊..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"做乜撚嘢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b6b060dd7fd87532277896e9ecda626366a184","tid":1986062,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T18:12:35.